STATE EX REL. SANDS
v.
CULOTTA 2018-1690 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 8, 2019

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellees' motion to strike appellant's brief. Motion denied. Appellees may file a merit brief within 30 days. Appellant's "motion to strike appellees' April 15, 2019 motion to strike" denied.
